{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "d4r-bbr-nerd-collective-api",
    "name": "TheNerdCollective.Integrations.Dar",
    "description": "HTTP API til DAR/BBR via Azure Functions.\n\nGuide: ../AZURE-FUNCTIONS-API.md\n\n**Sverre:** Start i mappen *Sverre — Autocomplete → KVHX* med `searchQueryOesterAlle` (adgangsadresse) eller `searchQueryOesterAlleUnit` (enhed).\n\nEnvironment:\n- baseUrl, functionKey\n- vej, postnr, by (klassisk opslag)\n- searchQueryOesterAlle, searchQueryOesterAlleUnit\n- autocompleteLocalId, autocompleteResultType, autocompleteHusnummerId (sættes af test-scripts)",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "auth": {
    "type": "apikey",
    "apikey": [
      { "key": "key", "value": "code", "type": "string" },
      { "key": "value", "value": "{{functionKey}}", "type": "string" },
      { "key": "in", "value": "query", "type": "string" }
    ]
  },
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Sverre — Autocomplete → KVHX",
      "description": "Anbefalet flow: SearchAsync → ResolveBestMatch → LookupFromAutocompleteAsync.\n\nKør requests 1→2 (adgangsadresse) eller 3→4 (enhed med etage/dør). Request *ét kald* kræver endpoint `/from-autocomplete` (se AZURE-FUNCTIONS-API.md).",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "1. Autocomplete — Øster Allé 48, 8260 Viby J",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "const results = pm.response.json();",
                  "const searchText = pm.variables.get('searchQueryOesterAlle');",
                  "function looksLikeUnit(s) { return /\\b\\d+\\s*(?:\\.?\\s*)?(?:sal|th|tv|mf|kl)\\b|\\b\\d+(?:th|sal|tv)\\b|\\b(?:st|kl|mf)\\b/i.test(s || ''); }",
                  "function isAdresse(r) { return (r.resultType || '').toLowerCase() === 'adresse'; }",
                  "function isHusnummer(r) { return (r.resultType || '').toLowerCase() === 'husnummer'; }",
                  "let valgt = null;",
                  "if (looksLikeUnit(searchText)) {",
                  "  valgt = results.find(r => r.isCompleteAddress && isAdresse(r))",
                  "    || results.find(r => r.isCompleteAddress)",
                  "    || results[0];",
                  "} else {",
                  "  valgt = results.find(r => r.isCompleteAddress && isHusnummer(r))",
                  "    || results.find(r => r.isCompleteAddress && isAdresse(r))",
                  "    || results.find(r => r.isCompleteAddress)",
                  "    || results[0];",
                  "}",
                  "pm.test('Autocomplete returnerede resultater', () => pm.expect(results.length).to.be.above(0));",
                  "pm.test('Bedste match fundet', () => pm.expect(valgt).to.be.an('object'));",
                  "if (valgt) {",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('autocompleteLocalId', valgt.localId);",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('autocompleteResultType', valgt.resultType || '');",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('autocompleteHusnummerId', valgt.husnummerId || valgt.localId);",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('autocompleteDisplayName', valgt.displayName || '');",
                  "  console.log('Valgt:', valgt.displayName, valgt.resultType, valgt.localId);",
                  "}"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{ "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/dar/autocomplete?q={{searchQueryOesterAlle}}",
            "description": "Første trin i Sverres Azure Function-flow. Test-script vælger bedste husnummer-match og gemmer LocalId/HusnummerId til næste request."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "2. KvHxInput from autocomplete (ét kald, q=)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{ "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/dar/adresseopslag/kvhx/from-autocomplete?q={{searchQueryOesterAlle}}",
            "description": "Svarer til LookupFromAutocompleteAsync + KvHxInput. Ét kald — SearchAsync, ResolveBestMatch og id-opslag på serveren.\n\nForventet: kvhxId for adgangsadresse (uden etage/dør)."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "2b. KvHxInput from autocomplete (med ids fra step 1)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{ "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/dar/adresseopslag/kvhx/from-autocomplete?localId={{autocompleteLocalId}}&resultType={{autocompleteResultType}}&husnummerId={{autocompleteHusnummerId}}&q={{searchQueryOesterAlle}}",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["dar", "adresseopslag", "kvhx", "from-autocomplete"],
              "query": [
                { "key": "localId", "value": "{{autocompleteLocalId}}" },
                { "key": "resultType", "value": "{{autocompleteResultType}}" },
                { "key": "husnummerId", "value": "{{autocompleteHusnummerId}}" },
                { "key": "q", "value": "{{searchQueryOesterAlle}}" }
              ]
            },
            "description": "Alternativ to-trins flow: kør request 1 først, derefter denne med ids fra autocomplete (ikke DisplayName)."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "3. Autocomplete — Øster Allé 48, 2. tv, 8260 Viby J",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "const results = pm.response.json();",
                  "const searchText = pm.variables.get('searchQueryOesterAlleUnit');",
                  "function looksLikeUnit(s) { return /\\b\\d+\\s*(?:\\.?\\s*)?(?:sal|th|tv|mf|kl)\\b|\\b\\d+(?:th|sal|tv)\\b|\\b(?:st|kl|mf)\\b/i.test(s || ''); }",
                  "function isAdresse(r) { return (r.resultType || '').toLowerCase() === 'adresse'; }",
                  "function isHusnummer(r) { return (r.resultType || '').toLowerCase() === 'husnummer'; }",
                  "let valgt = null;",
                  "if (looksLikeUnit(searchText)) {",
                  "  valgt = results.find(r => r.isCompleteAddress && isAdresse(r))",
                  "    || results.find(r => r.isCompleteAddress)",
                  "    || results[0];",
                  "} else {",
                  "  valgt = results.find(r => r.isCompleteAddress && isHusnummer(r))",
                  "    || results.find(r => r.isCompleteAddress && isAdresse(r))",
                  "    || results.find(r => r.isCompleteAddress)",
                  "    || results[0];",
                  "}",
                  "pm.test('Autocomplete returnerede resultater', () => pm.expect(results.length).to.be.above(0));",
                  "if (valgt) {",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('autocompleteLocalId', valgt.localId);",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('autocompleteResultType', valgt.resultType || '');",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('autocompleteHusnummerId', valgt.husnummerId || valgt.localId);",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('autocompleteDisplayName', valgt.displayName || '');",
                  "}"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{ "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/dar/autocomplete?q={{searchQueryOesterAlleUnit}}",
            "description": "Enhedsadresse — forvent ResultType `adresse` med HusnummerId ≠ LocalId."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "4. KvHxInput from autocomplete — enhed (ét kald)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "const kvhx = pm.response.json();",
                  "pm.test('Etage udfyldt', () => pm.expect(kvhx.etage).to.eql('2'));",
                  "pm.test('Dør udfyldt', () => pm.expect(kvhx.dør || kvhx.dor).to.eql('tv'));",
                  "pm.test('KVHX-id for enhed', () => pm.expect(kvhx.kvhxId).to.eql('07519554__48__2__tv'));"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{ "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/dar/adresseopslag/kvhx/from-autocomplete?q={{searchQueryOesterAlleUnit}}",
            "description": "Forventet KvHxInput med etage=`2`, dør=`tv`, kvhxId=`07519554__48__2__tv`."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "5. Full lookup from autocomplete (BBR-kæde)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{ "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/lookup/full/from-autocomplete?q={{searchQueryOesterAlle}}",
            "description": "Samlet BBR-opslag via autocomplete-valg (id-baseret adresseopslag + bygninger/enheder m.m.)."
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Lookup",
      "description": "Samlet opslag og opsummering — svarer til knappen \"Test alle services\" og Opsummering-sektionen.",
      "item": [
